headline: "Running a Restaurant Is No Joke": Square’s New Campaign, Featuring Actor and Foodie Eric Wareheim, Highlights Restaurants’ Hard-Earned Insights
summary: LOS ANGELES, February 10, 2025--Today, Square released a new video series, "Running a Restaurant Is No Joke," that features actor, winemaker, and comedian Eric Wareheim in four humorous and insightful episodes that dive into the grit and substance it takes to open and run a restaurant.
